Uses of Package
de.wwu.muggl.instructions.replaced

Packages that use de.wwu.muggl.instructions.replaced
de.wwu.muggl.instructions.replaced Provides the packages for the quick instructions and the replacers that set them along with the two interfaces for replacer and quick instructions. 
de.wwu.muggl.instructions.replaced.quick Provides QuickInstruction classes which can be used to speed up execution. 
de.wwu.muggl.instructions.replaced.replacer Provides ReplacingInstruction classes that can be used to set QuickInstruction classes. 
de.wwu.muggl.vm.classfile.structures Provides the representations for structures to be encountered in a classfile. 
de.wwu.muggl.vm.classfile.structures.attributes Provides the representations for structures used by attributes of a classfile. 
 

Classes in de.wwu.muggl.instructions.replaced used by de.wwu.muggl.instructions.replaced
ReplacingInstruction
          Interface for classes that extend instruction classes in order to enable them to be replaced by their quick versions.
 

Classes in de.wwu.muggl.instructions.replaced used by de.wwu.muggl.instructions.replaced.quick

          Interface for classes representing a java bytecode instruction that can be used to replace other instructions at runtime to optimize execution speed.
